data.description: Welcome to this 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom ranch-style residence. This cozy home offers comfortable living spaces with a spacious backyard for relaxation and gatherings. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, downsizing, or seeking a charming place to call your own, this property is the perfect fit. Plus, it's conveniently walkable to schools and outdoor recreational opportunities, making it an even more enticing choice. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!Updates include New Siding-2021, Furnace and A/C refurbished 2019, New Windows and exterior doors-2019, New well pump and holding tank-2022, New water filtration system 2020, and New garage door-2022.
